HEADWORD: Impend
<hw>Im*pend"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>impend⟦ecr⟧re</ets>; pref. <ets>im-</ets> in +
<ets>pend⟦ecr⟧re</ets> to weigh out, pay.]</ety> <def>To pay.</def>
