<p><ent>Impend</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Impend
<hw>Im*pend"</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. & p. p.</pos>
<conjf>Impended</conjf>; <pos>p. pr. & vb. n.</pos>
<conjf>Impending</conjf>.]</vmorph> <ety>[L. <ets>impend⟦emac⟧re</ets>;
pref. <ets>im-</ets> in + <ets>pend⟦emac⟧re</ets> to hang. See
<er>Pendant</er>.]</ety> <def>To hang over; to be suspended above; to
threaten from near at hand; to menace; to be imminent. See
<er>Imminent</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Destruction sure o'er all your heads <qex>impends</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Pope.</qau></rj></p>

<p><ent>Impendency</ent>⟦br⟧
